---
title: Buffalo-Tossed Shrimp with Ranch and Sweet Potato Wedges
description: Buttery buffalo shrimp get sandwiched between toasty brioche and slathered in ranch in tonight's pub grub-inspired recipe. A side of sweet potato wedges brings the dish together!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sandwichs-aux-crevettes-style-buffalo-e6b491ef.jpg
